          "prompt": "## Conditional Logic Decision Result\n\n**Input Value:** {{ value }}\n\n**Condition Checks:**\n- Greater than 100? {{ gt_100 }}\n- Less than 50? {{ lt_50 }}\n- Combined (OR): {{ combined }}\n- Route Decision: {{ route }}\n\n**Processing Path:**\n{{ processing }}\n\n**Decision Logic:**\nThis workflow demonstrates:\n- Deriving a boolean from a number with PadText + Compare + Equals\n- If-pair convergence as an if/else select\n- If-pair convergence as an OR gate\n- Nested conditional branching\n- Result aggregation"
        },
